column16: Michael Lorenzen grounds out softly, pitcher John Gant to first baseman Matt Carpenter.
Tucker Barnhart flies out to left fielder Jose Martinez.
Jose Peraza strikes out on a foul tip.
Patrick Kivlehan flies out to center fielder Tommy Pham.
Scooter Gennett homers (6) on a fly ball to left field.
Eugenio Suarez called out on strikes.
Joey Votto flies out to left fielder Jose Martinez.
Zack Cozart singles on a sharp line drive to left fielder Jose Martinez.   Billy Hamilton to 2nd.
Tim Adleman grounds out, first baseman Matt Carpenter to pitcher John Gant.
Tucker Barnhart flies out to left fielder Jose Martinez.
Jose Peraza grounds into a force out, shortstop Paul DeJong to second baseman Greg Garcia.   Patrick Kivlehan out at 2nd.
Scooter Gennett homers (5) on a line drive to center field.   Eugenio Suarez scores.
